From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Aneesh Pradhan <aneeshpradhan@acm.org>
Date: Wed, 22 Jul 2026 22:10:00 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: dts: qcom: perry: enable rear dw9718s AF

Wire the Dongwoon DW9718S VCM on CCI0 for rear autofocus. Stock
libactuator_dw9718s.so uses 8-bit slave 0x18 (7-bit 0x0c) with VAF on
pm8937_l22. Mainline drivers/media/i2c/dw9719.c already matches
compatible "dongwoon,dw9718s" (tested on motorola-nora).

lens-focus on the rear S5K4H8 node is consumed by
v4l2_async_register_subdev_sensor().

Signed-off-by: Aneesh Pradhan <aneeshpradhan@acm.org>
---
 .../qcom/msm8917-motorola-perry-common.dtsi   | 16 ++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 16 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/msm8917-motorola-perry-common.dtsi b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/msm8917-motorola-perry-common.dtsi
index 16ac04e..a1b2c3d 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/msm8917-motorola-perry-common.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/msm8917-motorola-perry-common.dtsi
@@ -653,6 +653,18 @@ &cci_i2c0 {
 	#address-cells = <1>;
 	#size-cells = <0>;
 
+	/*
+	 * Rear AF: Dongwoon DW9718S. Stock 8-bit write address 0x18 →
+	 * 7-bit 0x0c. VAF = pm8937_l22 @ 2.8 V.
+	 */
+	dw9718s: lens@c {
+		compatible = "dongwoon,dw9718s";
+		reg = <0x0c>;
+		vdd-supply = <&pm8937_l22>;
+		/* Binding default; SAC3 matches driver DW9718S_DEFAULT_SAC. */
+		dongwoon,sac-mode = <4>;
+	};
+
 	/*
 	 * Rear camera: Samsung S5K4H8. Stock 8-bit write address 0x5A →
 	 * 7-bit 0x2d. Chip id 0x4088 @ reg 0x0000 (libmmcamera_s5k4h8.so).
@@ -670,6 +682,8 @@ &cci_i2c0 {
 		avdd-supply = <&cam_vana_2v8>;
 		dovdd-supply = <&cam_vio_1v8>;
 		dvdd-supply = <&pm8937_l23>;
+
+		lens-focus = <&dw9718s>;
 
 		port {
 			s5k4h8_ep: endpoint {
-- 
2.53.0
